Fix some Reverb2 High Samplerate problems. (#6171)

Run reverb2 at 48000 * 32 khz and it would crash. Now it just
mis-renders the reverb some insted. Make sure the buffers
are sized to avoid clipping upto 48k * 8 (382) though.

Don't use sample rates that high! But surge should never crash.